company_name: JOSEF VONACH, VIEH- UND FLEISCHGROSSHANDEL GESELLSCHAFT M.B.H. & CO. KG.
information: The company JOSEF VONACH, VIEH- UND FLEISCHGROSSHANDEL GESELLSCHAFT M.B.H. & CO. KG., is a Wholesaler, founded in 1962, which operates in the Meat industry. It also operates in the Livestock - import-export, and Meat cutting industries. It is based in Lauterach, Austria.
